data.description: Gorgeous Home on Oversized fenced lot. 3/3 plus Den, No expense has been spared! Features Impact doors and windows, High ceilings, open floor plan, imported Porcelain tile floors, Large kitchen with island, quartz counters and top of the line Stainless Steel appliances. Formal Dining, tasteful barn doors open to useful den. Huge Master bedroom with his and hers walk-in closets, Master Bath has dual sinks with matching quartz counters , a specious Shower with double rain shower head, tiled to ceiling and enclosed with frameless glass. Immense screened lanai that is tiled and has 2 ceiling fans, Laundry room with washer/dryer. Garage for 2 cars with remote opener and much, much more. centrally located close to schools, shopping and dining. Priced for a quick sale. Easy to see.
